parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration of the vehicle can lead to accidents, loss of control, and potential harm to the driver and passengers.
symptoms: The vehicle surges or lunges forward without warning
even when the brake pedal is depressed. This can occur when the air conditioning is on
when driving at low speeds
or when shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or experience unintended acceleration, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
especially when the air conditioning is on. The throttle body may stick
causing the engine to surge or rev unexpectedly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the CVT transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and surge forward, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle surges forward
loses power
stalls
and has difficulty shifting gears. The wrench light and check engine light may illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body transmission can cause the vehicle to surge forward, lose power, and stall, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle surges forward
loses power
stalls
and has difficulty shifting gears. The wrench light and check engine light may illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch hydraulic system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and surge forward, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle surges forward
loses power
stalls
and has difficulty shifting gears. The wrench light and check engine light may illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body can cause the vehicle to surge or lunge forward, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle surges or lunges forward when idling or driving
the engine RPM increases without pressing the accelerator
the vehicle stalls
and the check engine light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates without pressing the accelerator
surges forward
and lunges backward when in reverse.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The air conditioning system can cause the throttle body to malfunction, leading to unintended acceleration and loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle surges or lunges forward when the air conditioning is turned on
and the engine RPM increases without pressing the accelerator.
